# Download genome annotation files or SRA data from NCBI ftp

## Examples

1. Download one genome by full name

ascp_download.pl -t bac -o out Mycobacterium_JDM601_uid67369

2. search multiple genomes, from a id list

ascp_download.pl -t bac -o out bac.list

3. Download genomes with part name: (H37Rv, NC_000962)

ascp_download.pl -t bac -o out -d bacteria.info -m search  H37Rv

4. Download SRA data by specific ID: SRR/ERR/DRR

ascp_download.pl -t sra -o out SRR123456

or from a id.list

ascp_download.pl -t sra -o out sra.list

